"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-sport-olympics-inside-paris-2024-olympic-village-3183537\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE Account James Gray gets a sneak preview of the apartments that will house nearly 15,000 athletes competing at this summer's Olympic Games PARIS - AsOlympicathletes start arriving in Paris forthe biggest sporting event on earth, they may be concerned to discover their rooms do not have air-conditioning.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3686816891996459e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NEWS\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"Account James Gray\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 54}, {\"ngram\": \"a sneak preview\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 15,000 athletes\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Olympic Games PARIS - AsOlympicathletes\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 199}, {\"ngram\": \"biggest sporting event\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"their rooms\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"air-conditioning\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Average July and August highs in the French capital reach around 26\\u00b0C, but heatwaves can send the mercury north of 40, as it has done twice in the last five summers.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9648538551952056, \"rank\": 0.029202948482091075, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Average July and August highs\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"around 26\\u00b0C\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"heatwaves\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"the mercury north\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"the last five summers\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Villagewill be home to nearly 15,000 athletes, a unique community that the temporary residents often report as one of the best experiences of any Games - but extreme heat could turn that into a nightmare.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Villagewill\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 15,000 athletes\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique community\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary residents\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"the best experiences\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"any Games\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme heat\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"a nightmare\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of conventional air-conditioning units, each apartment is fitted with a water-based cooling system in the walls, which can lower the room temperature by as much as 10\\u00b0C, while authorities will rely on the design of the buildings and advice to those on higher floors to keep blinds and windows closed during the day to assist with cooling.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"conventional air-conditioning units\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"each apartment\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"a water-based cooling system\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the walls\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the room temperature\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"as much as 10\\u00b0C\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"the design\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"higher floors\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"blinds\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"windows\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A brand new geothermal station behind the temporary transport mall will bring hot temperature [water] during the winter for the whole area,\\\" says Laurent Michaud, the director of the Olympic & Paralympic Village, explaining that a 70-metre well provides water for the climate control system.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A brand new geothermal station\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary transport mall\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"hot temperature\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole area\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"Laurent Michaud\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"the director\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"a 70-metre well\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate control system\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The water is around 14\\u00b0C.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"around 14\\u00b0C\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's actually pumped and injected into some stations into the ground floors of the buildings, and then it goes into the apartments.\\\"\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some stations\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground floors\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As many as 300Team GBathletes and performance staff will stay in some of the village's 2,807 apartments at any one time during the Games, where they may also be surprised to find thermostats that only raise or lower the temperature by two degrees, rather than setting the temperature independently.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"300Team GBathletes\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"performance staff\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the village's 2,807 apartments\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"any one time\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"thermostats\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"the temperature\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"two degrees\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"the temperature\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The thermostat can reduce or accelerate the water in the pipe system, but the biggest setting is made in the stations at the ground floor of the buildings,\\\" Michaud explains.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The thermostat\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"the pipe system\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest setting\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"the stations\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground floor\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"Michaud\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The communal areas of the apartment buildings will have conventional air-conditioning.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The communal areas\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartment buildings\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"conventional air-conditioning\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers also believe that the street layout design will promote cooler air from the River Seine up the wide streets to the residential areas, as will the 9,000 trees and shrubs planted around the site.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2184, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"the street layout design\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"cooler air\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"the wide streets\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"the residential areas\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"the 9,000 trees\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"shrubs\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2003, 15,000 died in France during a heatwave, attributed in part to the lack of shade in the city which drove temperatures higher.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999997698978, \"rank\": 1.9455927963288235e-10, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heatwave\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"shade\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"temperatures\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even now, only around 10 per cent of Paris is taken up by green spaces, compared to 33 per cent in London.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3686816891996459e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999557257989, \"rank\": 4.4267999549264946e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only around 10 per cent\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"green spaces\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"33 per cent\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"iwas given access to one of the apartments that will house athletes and some support staff, with a peak of around 300 Team GB athletes staying there at any one time during the Games.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"some support staff\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"a peak\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"any one time\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conditions on the day were not swelteringly hot, so it was hard to ascertain whether the new air-cooling systems really did work as officials insist they will.\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conditions\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"the new air-cooling systems\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The apartments are hardly palatial, with athletes sharing rooms and sleeping in single beds, which are bedecked with Paris 2024-branded duvets, which Olympians and Paralympians can take home as a souvenir.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.736600791558889e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The apartments\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"rooms\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"single beds\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"-branded duvets\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympians\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"a souvenir\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Otherwise, these \\\"homes from home\\\" are deliberately sparse.\", \"